title: Start
tags: example, night in the woods style,
body:
Amy: Well, look at this!
Joe: Yes, it's Night in the Woods style scripting.
Amy: How cool! And the way it works, you get the speaker name and the text.
Joe: Nice! So you can make speech bubbles?
Amy: Yup! Or you can add avatars. Or character busts. Any number of things?
Joe: SAWEET.
Amy: You can even add a choice. Wanna see?
Joe: Okay. Sure!
Amy: CHOOSE WISELY.
[[ answer: |Jump Jump]]

title: Jump Jump
body:
Amy: Jump party time!
Joe: oh now. I don't want to.
Amy: Why not?
Joe: because I don't want to be a jumping joe.
Amy: Figures.

title: stand like a fool
body:
Amy: You fool! Why did you choose this one?
Joe: Come on, don't be so mean.
